# Exercise 002 - Exposing your database application

1) As developer, deploy again your mysql application from template

2) Verify if the DeploymentConfig, Pods and Service are up and running;

3) Remove the service related to mysql;

4) Write a new yaml to create a NodePort which responds to port 30036;
   then create the new object on the cluster;

5) Verify the new service, the oc status output and the service specifications;

6) From the Minishift vm, try to reach the NodePort service on your
   cluster IP and on your node ip;
